<h3 id="recommended-textbook">Recommended Textbook</h3>

<ul>
  <li>&lt; Real-Time Rendering&gt;</li>
  <li>&lt; Computer Graphics: Principles and Practice&gt;, 2nd Edition (3rd would be released around mid 2013) 	- &lt; Computer Graphics, C Version&gt;, 2nd Edition (not 3rd or 4th)</li>
  <li>&lt; Fundamentals of Computer Graphics&gt;, 3rd Edition</li>
  <li>&lt; Computer Graphics using OpenGL&gt;, 2nd or 3rd Edition*</li>
  <li>&lt; Interactive Computer Graphics: A Top-Down Approach with Shader-Based OpenGL&gt;, 6th Edition</li>
  <li>&lt; 3D Computer Graphics: A Mathematical Introduction with OpenGL&gt;</li>
</ul>
